How Germany’s Der Spiegel uses games, comments to boost engagement
description: 2025-05-06. One of the major themes of WAN-IFRA's World News Media Congress 2025 is how publishers deepen relationships with audiences through high-engagement products and features. title: Mesa firefighter passes away while on duty
description: Mesa Fire and Medical Department officials say identified the firefighter who passed away as Mark Keller, who has been with the department for decades.

title: EMGS: Summons for written resolution in relation to Elec ASA 18/25 FRN USD FLOOR STEP C CONV
description: Reference is made to the stock exchange notification published by Electromagnetic Geoservices ASA ("EMGS" or the "Company") on 6 May 2025 regarding the Siem Day transaction, including the information therein regarding a proposed extension of the maturity date for Elec ASA 18/25 FRN USD FLOOR STEP C CONV (“EMGS03”) as well as certain other proposed amendments to the bond terms related to the transaction.
